String::Charcount
=================

Extension that counts the occurence of characters within a string.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install
   
SCRIPTS

bin/count.pl

Interface to String::Charcount that contains 
predefined options and outputs counted characters.

